quran[12]{c,v,t,f}:
  26,121,"Chisimu mu yalakweyi mwana chilosyo, nambo ŵajinji mwa ŵanganyao nganaŵa ŵakulupilila."
  26,122,"Soni chisimu Ambuje ŵenu ni ŵali Ŵamachili gakupunda, Ŵachanasa channope."
  26,123,"Achina Adi ŵakaaniile achimitenga."
  28,67,"Nambo mundu jwatesile toba ni kulupilila ni kutendaga soni yambone, basi jwalakwe tachiŵa mwa ŵandu ŵakupunda."
  28,68,"Sano Ambuje ŵenu akasagumba chaakusaka ni kusagula (chaakusaka). Nganakola ŵanganyao kusagula kulikose. Aswejele Allah, soni atukwiche kwannope ku yaakum’bwanganya nayo."
  28,69,"Soni Ambuje ŵenu akuimanyilila yaikusisa mitima jao ni yaakuilochesya papaswela."
  29,34,"“Chisimu uwwe tusigele panandi kwatuluchisya achinsyene awu musi (wa Sodomu) ipotesi kutyochela kwinani ligongo lya kunyosya kwao.”"
  29,35,"Soni chisimu pamasile patwalesile mwalakwemo chimanyilo chakuonechela kwa ŵandu ŵaakwete lunda."
  29,36,"Sano (kuŵandu ŵa) ku Madiyana (twantumisye) nnongo n’jao (jwali) Shuaibu. Basi jwatite: “E ŵandu ŵangu! Mun’galagatilani Allah, ni llijogope Lisiku Lyambesi, soni nkajendagajendaga pa chilambo kupita nchiwatanganya.”"
  30,13,"Ni ngasakola ŵanganyao akuchondelela kuumila mwa akwawanganya ŵao (ni Allah), ni tachiŵa (akwawanganya ŵaowo yaili isanamu) ŵakwakana akuwanganya ŵao."
  30,14,"Sano lisiku lyajichijima Kiyama, lyele lisikulyo ŵanganyao tachilekangana (ŵane wa ku Mbepo ŵane wa ku Moto)."
  30,15,"Basi aŵala ŵaakulupilile ni kutendaga yambone tachiŵa mu Litimbe lyakusangalasya (lya ku Mbepo) ali nkusengwasyidwa."